  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UK funding to PMEH specifically supports support 1) procurement of air quality monitoring equipment in seven middle-income countries, to provide a more accurate picture of the scale and structure of air pollution and 2) establish and build on existing digital platforms for the dissemination of knowledge in relation to air pollution, including both the level of pollution but also policy solutions.</narrative>
  </description>
